		<title>06SEA ANGLING, BOATING - ARRAN</title>
		<content> The Arran Sea Angling Centre is       
 situated on the beach in Brodick.     
                                       
   Fishing dinghies with Seagull 40    
 plus outboard motors are for hire by  
 the day or half day.  Rowing dinghies 
 are also available for hire by the    
 hour.  The season lasts from Easter   
 until September.                      
                                       
   On a fishing trip you may catch     
 herring, mackerel, salmon, trout or   
 cod in the bay.  The best baits are   
 cockles and lugworm.                  
                                       
   The best areas for fishing are off  
 Merkland Point or round the bay       
 towards the pier.                     
                                       
                                       
                                       
